  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two naval ships rushed from the port of Colombo!",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Two ships of the Sri Lanka Navy, Gajapahu and Sinthurala, which were anchored in the port of Colombo, have departed from there with some goods and personnel.",
        "A video has been shared on social media showing some people carrying luggage into the ship at a high speed at the port of Colombo.",
        "However, it is noteworthy that although the media asked the port master (harbor master) about who went on these ships and what were the goods transported, he said that he did not know about it."
      ],
